# 12. Visual style

For your apps, I would not start with traditional pixel art.

## Better v1 style

Use simple SVG illustration.

Why:

* lighter
* scalable
* looks cleaner on iPad/browser
* easier to recolour
* easier to animate with CSS
* simpler for multiple app themes

## Animation list

Only a few are needed:

* idle bob
* blink
* happy bounce
* sleepy droop
* proud sparkle
* worried wobble

